&lt;p&gt;Applications are invited for a full-time locum consultant immunologist with an interest in allergy or a consultant allergist. You will be joining one of the leading Immunology centres in the UK, which is accredited by the QPIDS scheme of the Royal College of Physicians and recognised as an international Centre of Excellence by the Federation of Clinical Immunology Societies. The department provides a wide-ranging service encompassing primary and secondary immunodeficiency, complex allergy, immunotherapy and systemic autoimmune disease. This post is in addition to a substantive post due to be advertised later this year.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Salary: £82,096.00 - £110,683.00&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Closing date: 6th November 2020&lt;/p&gt;
